# Google Play Data Safety Draft

## Data collection
Default answer: The app does not collect data by default.

## Data stored on device
TalkFreeAAC stores AAC communication data locally on the user's device.

Local data may include:
- Communication history
- Completed sentences
- Word usage
- Favorites
- Recents
- Emergency profile
- Accessibility settings
- Parent/team notes if enabled

## Data sharing
Default: No data is shared by default.

## Optional export
Parents may export local backup files. Exported files are controlled by the user.

## Optional future sync
If future sync is added, it must be opt-in and parent-controlled.
